description: Tawfic Abdel Jabbar, 17, was killed in the Israeli-occupied West Bank on Friday, his family said.
maintext: At least 319 Palestinians have been killed in the West Bank since the war broke out on 7 October, according to UN data. Many were killed in shootouts with the Israeli military, but some, witnesses say, were killed by Israeli forces and settlers while they were unarmed.
title: US demands Israel conduct full investigation into Palestinian-American teen's killing
